name: Jinu ❤️
greetingText: I really like your name baby
wishText: Hey lusu, I am very Lucky to have u in my life. Thanks for staying with me. I still don't know why u are loving me this much nu. I'll care u as a newborn hand baby di. My favorite sound in the universe is your laugh. If you keep being so sweet, I'll have diabetes very soon 😂😂😂. I assure u that i will be ur good husband as well as a good friend forever ❤️. Po di lusu
